channel.title: Proxy lists :)
channel.description:
Well, I diddent see an off-topic or misc. board... So I guess i'll just post these here... I descided to refresh my proxy lists... So I supose i'll share them :D I have... 89 High anonymous proxies 81 anonymous proxies and, 697 Transparent proxies, All working as of 4-25. I've also attached my java proxy parser for ACCESSDIVER "detailed" proxy list. It cuts out all the useless shit, and only leaves the ip, port, and ping time. (All you do is edit the run.bat for input/output file.)
Proxyparser.rar HAS the attached proxy files in it... So if you download the proxyparser.rar, theres no need to download the additional 3 text files :)
-Dr Blunt
